Use the standard library
This is how to parse_music of music_string:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that token is ""
   Remember that n is music_string's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that c is item i in music_string
      When c is " ", then:
         When token's length is more than 0, then:
            Add result to token's length
            Remember that token is ""
         End when
      But, if not:
         Add token to c
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   When token's length is more than 0, then:
      Add result to token's length
   End when
   The answer is result
Now you know
>>> parse_music of "" 
[]
>>> parse_music of "o o o o" 
[1, 1, 1, 1]
>>> parse_music of "oooo o oo" 
[4, 1, 2]
>>> parse_music of "  oo   oooo  o " 
[2, 4, 1]